result.name: Leung Lee Restaurant

reviews.text:
Is very local restaurant. Do not expect superior dishes and interior. Is just plain local style and taste. No English menu or speaking either. I would suggest to tourists however. Since this is the style we have in the past 30 years here.
Is specially great for breakfast. It may be difficult to locate after the street market open at around 11
Typical local style cafe. Small and compact, good milk tea. Great for tea time.

Like many have already said - don't expect something out of the blue. It's a basic Hong Kong breakfast restaurant, and that's as much as it is. Their Bo Loh Bai is quite nice and buttery - but you'll have to eat it warm or else it's absolutely average.
Serve with a broken dish.
除奶茶及包類外就無樣好食，奶茶仲要幾次飲到上手的檸檬核

result.name: 兩利餐廳

reviews.text: 除奶茶及包類外就無樣好食，奶茶仲要幾次飲到上手的檸檬核
旺角區內歷史最老的茶餐廳，食物質素ㄧ般，但懷舊風味甚濃。
紙包蛋糕，卷蛋，港式馬卡龍都有水準！少有嘅茶走走花奶⋯沒有一點點👍🏼老師傅果然不同

各樣餐點口味中上，份量很多。服務大叔遇到台灣人很熱情，用餐環境也很道地，很棒的小店。
ps店裡辣油太香了！！！要哪裡才買得到呢～
有人情味街坊餐廳。
